        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1061",
        "content": "mrs Bird thought, as the music floated in upon her gentle sleep, that she had slipped into heaven with her new baby, and that the angels were bidding them welcome.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
