        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1061",
        "content": "It looked like a rose dipped in milk, she thought, this pink and white blossom of girlhood, or like a pink cherub, with its halo of pale yellow hair, finer than floss silk.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
