        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1061",
        "content": "\"I think it is a charming name, dear heart, and that it sounds just like you, and I hope that, being a girl, this baby has some chance of being as lovely as her mother,\" at which speech from the baby's papa, mrs Bird, though she was as weak and tired as she could be, blushed with happiness.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
